# Wi-Fi Attacks Lab

## Objective
Evaluate wireless security through packet capture, deauthentication, and WPA/WPA2 cracking techniques.

## Tools Used
- Aircrack-ng  
- Airodump-ng  
- Wireshark  

## Steps
1. Captured Wi-Fi packets  
2. Performed deauthentication attack  
3. Attempted WPA/WPA2 handshake cracking  

## Key Learnings
- Wi-Fi encryption weaknesses  
- Importance of strong passphrases  
- Network segmentation improves safety  
